{"tid":597859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★立法會檢討綜援計劃 出席人士要求增加綜援金額 !!","createTime":"2018-03-19T04:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T10:39:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77d7e58b5de6e58c5367c06c5eec7a91c2b95d7a","tid":597859,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"立法會福利事務委員會召開特別會議，檢討綜援計劃。有出席的公眾人士要求政府<span style=\"color: red;\">增加綜援金額</span>，及讓長者和殘疾人士以個人為單位申請綜援。<br />\n<br />\n殘疾人士王芷欣表示：「今年二月加了五十五元，在我的個案，五十五元可以做甚麼？<span style=\"color: red;\">拿綜援五千多元</span>，每間院舍都不肯收我，我怎樣堅持到維持每日生活？現時院舍是收六千多元、六千五百元、七千五百元，傷津又沒有，還要兩元乘車優惠都申請不到，你叫我做甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n自強協會輪友關注政策小組成員楊鳳儀說：「現時家庭為單位申請綜援制度，令不少有經濟需要，與家人同住的長者及殘疾人士都不能申領綜援。可獨立申請綜援，以保障他們的生活環境和質素。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5aaf2481e60383bc4210ce0f/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5aaf2481e60383bc4210ce0f%2F&d=TMpmTYxyytHSiUfDdv5QnzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=d7b90152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5aaf2481e60383bc4210ce0f/</a>"},{"pid":"ecf2edeec3b92802bdfe1dac56953f296d0033f8","tid":597859,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf1be85111c000ab3a6ac4ec720678cbfc967a2","tid":597859,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd84c0fef63c1b65e7b3d2e53036775d4898db6","tid":597859,"uid":11523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:27:19.000Z","msg":"殘疾人士拎唔到傷殘津貼？<br />\n一係審批有問題<br />\n一係佢唔係殘疾囉<br />\n講乜鳩"},{"pid":"d68b816b739a988551e